Install:
Copy the bsp file in youre cstrike/maps directory.

##################################################

Updates in Beta3:

#Added Overview
#Fixed several Bugs
#Added a new house
#Added new Textures
#Added a complete self-textured secret room
#Fixed Gameplay at some unfair Spots
#Changed complete lighting to a darker Brightness
#Added several sprites
#Optimized Map with Nodraw and func_details for more FPS
#Included some Sounds
#Added some Decals
#Changed the 3D Sky

##################################################

Overall I can say it looks nicer and better than before,
its Optimized Pretty Good Now and its very well balanced in this version.
Dont care about the picture of the Overview, it looks crappy but
you can see how the Map is built.

If you can't find the Secret Room message me ;D

##################################################


Have fun with the Map.
Greetingz BaShoR
